00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:02.700
and manipulated by Liu Sinan.

00:04:04.600 --> 00:04:06.000
Thank you, Young Master.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:07.450
Young Mistress.

00:04:08.760 --> 00:04:09.600
I

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:13.330
take my leave. Where are you going?

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:42.800
Who?

00:04:45.159 --> 00:04:46.240
It's you.

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:48.180
Didn't I tell you to stay far away?

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:49.320
Why did you come back?

00:04:49.320 --> 00:04:50.240
I came back

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:51.320
to take your life.

00:04:53.159 --> 00:04:54.020
Are you insane?

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:55.240
I already told you,

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:57.159
