00:05:03.200 --> 00:05:04.200
Liu Sinan.

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:05.530
I was such a fool.

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:07.080
You deceived me for so long,

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:09.640
and I almost got the young master and his wife killed.

00:05:09.640 --> 00:05:10.800
Today I'm going to kill you

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:12.080
to avenge Xiuhe.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:13.640
Stop slandering me.

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.760
This is what Yiyu found in your room.

00:05:20.760 --> 00:05:22.220
What do you have to say now?

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:24.800
Why did you kill Xiuhe?

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:26.480
Tell me!

00:05:32.320 --> 00:05:33.250
She deserved it.

00:05:33.400 --> 00:05:34.520
What did you say?

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:36.520
She should never have

00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:38.860
It shouldn't have been there.

00:05:42.480 --> 00:05:44.680
On Liu Silin's 18th birthday,

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:47.920
I secretly took his jade pendant.

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:50.740
I didn't expect to run into Xiuhe.

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:53.400
She was going to tell my father.

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:58.159
I didn't really mean to kill her.

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:00.400
I just wanted to grab her

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:02.360
to stop her from going.

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:05.620
But she fell into the lake.

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:10.010
Then what about the gunshot wound on her head?

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:12.200
That was a few days later.

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:15.040
To frame Liu Silin,

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:17.080
I specifically had Commander Xu find

00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:18.680
that custom-made revolver.

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:20.850
At the same time,

00:06:21.400 --> 00:06:23.260
it would also clear my suspicion.

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:25.360
Liu Sinan,

00:06:25.880 --> 00:06:27.340
you're truly despicable.

00:06:27.640 --> 00:06:29.480
I can't believe that the dignified second young master of the Liu family

00:06:29.480 --> 00:06:31.140
would actually steal things.

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:37.770
It wasn't stealing.

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:39.600
It was taking.

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:40.960
Taking.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:44.400
Why?

00:06:45.159 --> 00:06:47.220
Why is it only on Liu Silin's birthday

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:48.680
that my father would call craftsmen from across the city

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:51.280
to make such an expensive jade pendant for him?

00:06:53.480 --> 00:06:57.159
Why would my father give him that custom-made revolver?

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:02.920
Why does everyone

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:04.240
in this household value him so much?

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:05.970
Just because he's legitimate?

00:07:09.640 --> 00:07:12.360
How am I, Liu Sinan, inferior to him?

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:14.360
I will take everything from him.

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:16.680
I'll make him miserable.

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:23.400
Yiyu.

00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:27.530
What are you doing here?

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:29.320
Today I finally know.

00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:33.040
So you're behind all these terrible things.

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.480
I'll kill you

00:07:35.640 --> 00:07:36.920
to avenge my parents.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:39.330
I didn't kill your parents.

00:07:39.480 --> 00:07:40.940
You're talking nonsense.

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:43.400
It's clear that you stole the jade pendant.

00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:44.760
